'''The Ten''' were a group of aristocratic families from all over the [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core Worlds]]. When the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] was formed, the Ten colonized the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Kuat/Legends|Kuat]], with the intent of creating the largest shipbuilding concern in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. They hired the best [[Terraforming/Legends|terraformers]] of the day to terraform Kuat into a paradise, creating a pleasant world with few predators. The Ten also succeeded in creating [[Kuat Drive Yards/Legends|Kuat Drive Yards]]. The Ten included:

*[[House Kuat]], the ruling family
*[[House Andrim]]
*[[House Depon]]
*[[House Knylenn]]
*[[House Kuhlvult]]
*[[House Purkis]]

